"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        Authentication structs with different credentials.
        """
a = contents.Authentication(credentials=[objects.Credential(credential_type
    =enums.CredentialType.USERNAME_AND_PASSWORD, credential_value=objects.
    UsernamePasswordCredential(username='Fred', password='password1'))])
b = contents.Authentication(credentials=[objects.Credential(credential_type
    =enums.CredentialType.DEVICE, credential_value=objects.DeviceCredential
    (device_serial_number='serNum123456', password='secret',
    device_identifier='devID2233', network_identifier='netID9000',
    machine_identifier='machineID1', media_identifier='mediaID313'))])
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
